nodes.text: Levet was a Mandalorian who owned a small farm on the planet Mandalore. Located near the capital city of Keldabe, it was situated just down a dirt road from the Beviin-Vasur farm.
While this Mandalorian's name is Levet, it is unknown if he was CC-3388/0021 given a new life by Kal Skirata or perhaps even a son.[source?]
